OL,6,FA multi-million pound indoor tennis
OL,7,Ffacility is set to be built in
OL,8,FDumfries.
OL,10,FThe three court facility is set to be
OL,11,Fbuilt at the King George V sport
OL,12,Fcomplex in Dumfries.
OL,14,F#1.7 million has been awarded by the
OL,15,FTransforming Scottish Indoor Tennis
OL,16,Ffund as well as #500k from Dumfries
OL,17,Fand Galloway Council and #200k from
OL,18,Fthe Holywood Trust.
