OL,6,FThe project is a collaboration between
OL,7,Fthe LTA, LTA Tennis Foundation,
OL,8,FSportScotland, Tennis Scotland and
OL,9,FDumfries and Galloway Council.
OL,11,FDumfries and Galloway Council Leader,
OL,12,FGail Macgregor said: "I'm delighted to
OL,13,Fsee this project moving forward.
OL,15,F"Our Council has committed half a
OL,16,Fmillion pounds towards the costs and
OL,17,Fthis clear commitment is a strong sign
OL,18,Fof the importance we place on this
OL,19,Ffacility, and indeed of facilities of
OL,20,Fits nature.
