OL,6,F"Having such an accessible facility in
OL,7,Four largest town in the region will
OL,8,Fnot only be excellent for local tennis
OL,9,Fplayers, but will attract people into
OL,10,Fthe region, boosting the local
OL,11,Feconomy. I look forward to seeing
OL,12,Fbuilding works commence."
OL,14,FThe facility will feature three indoor
OL,15,Fhard courts and is scheduled to open
OL,16,Fin 2025.
OL,18,FThe plans will also include a raised
OL,19,Fviewing area, office space and
OL,20,Faccessible changing areas.
