OL,6,FChief Executive of sportscotland,
OL,7,FForbes Dunlop, said: "This is another
OL,8,Fimportant development for tennis in
OL,9,FScotland. This new indoor tennis
OL,10,Fcentre in Dumfries is a fantastic
OL,11,Fexample of what can be delivered when
OL,12,Fwe work in partnership across the
OL,13,Fsporting sector.
OL,15,F"Our aim with the TSIT fund was to
OL,16,Fimprove year-round access to tennis in
OL,17,Fkey areas across Scotland and this is
OL,18,Fa significant milestone in that
OL,19,Fjourney.
